<h1 class="nhsuk-heading-xl">Invitation to tender</h1>

<p class="nhsuk-lead-paragraph">
  The {{ site.owner }} invites proposals from digital delivery partners to build a new digital
  service for personalised sickle cell care plans, for use during acute painful crises.
</p>

