<h2 class="nhsuk-heading-l">11. Terms</h2>
<ul class="nhsuk-list nhsuk-list--bullet">
  <li><strong>Intellectual property:</strong> outputs are intended to be fundamentally public domain, published under licences designed to maximise sharing and adoption. See <a class="nhsuk-link" href="{{ '/governance/' | url }}">governance</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Data protection:</strong> the contract will include provisions ensuring full compliance with UK GDPR and NHS data security requirements.</li>
  <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> we expect delivery in the open, with regular show-and-tells and published code.</li>
</ul>

